data.description: Rare opportunity to own in Rapputak, the most exclusive development on Lovewell Pond. Gorgeous homes throughout this waterfront community. Walk to the beautiful sandy beach and launch your boat. The views are absolutely breathtaking from everywhere you stand. Also known as Lovewell Lake this body of water is connected to the Saco River allowing you access to miles and miles of paddling. Fryeburg Center is 3 miles away, the attractions of N. Conway NH are just a 20 minute ride and Portland is under an hour away. It is time to build that home you have been dreaming about!
